PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,FKing Charles has delivered an historic
OL,7,Fspeech to both the House of
OL,8,FRepresentatives and the Senate, the
OL,9,Ftwo houses of the US Congress, at the
OL,10,FCapitol in Washington DC.
OL,12,FIn doing so he becomes only the second
OL,13,FBritish monarch to address Congress -
OL,14,Ffollowing in his mother's footsteps
OL,15,Fafter Queen Elizabeth became the first
OL,16,Fduring a state visit to the US in 1991.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,FHere is the full text of the King's
OL,7,Fspeech to Congress:
OL,9,F"Mr Vice President, Mr Speaker,
OL,10,Fmembers of Congress, representatives
OL,11,Fof the American people across all
OL,12,Fstates, territories, cities and
OL,13,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"I would like, if I may, to take this
OL,7,Fopportunity to express my particular
OL,8,Fgratitude to you all for the great
OL,9,Fhonour of addressing this joint
OL,10,Fmeeting of Congress and, on behalf of
OL,11,Fthe Queen and myself, to thank the
OL,12,FAmerican people for welcoming us to
OL,13,Fthe United States to mark this semi
OL,14,Fquincentennial year of the Declaration
OL,15,Fof Independence.
OL,17,F"And for all of that time, our
OL,18,Fdestinies as nations have been
OL,19,Finterlinked.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"As Oscar Wilde said, 'We have really
OL,7,Feverything in common with America
OL,8,Fnowadays except, of course, language'.
OL,10,F"So, ladies and gentlemen, we meet in
OL,11,Ftimes of great uncertainty, in times
OL,12,Fof conflict from Europe to the Middle
OL,13,FEast which pose immense challenges for
OL,14,Fthe international community and whose
OL,15,Fimpact is felt in communities the
OL,16,Flength and breadth of our own
OL,17,Fcountries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"We meet, too, in the aftermath of the
OL,7,Fincident not far from this great
OL,8,Fbuilding that sought to harm the
OL,9,Fleadership of your nation and to
OL,10,Ffoment wider fear and discord.
OL,12,F"Let me say with unshakeable resolve:
OL,13,Fsuch acts of violence will never
OL,14,Fsucceed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"Whatever our differences, whatever
OL,7,Fdisagreements we may have, we stand
OL,8,Funited in our commitment to uphold
OL,9,Fdemocracy, to protect all our people
OL,10,Ffrom harm, and to salute the courage
OL,11,Fof those who daily risk their lives in
OL,12,Fthe service of our countries.
OL,14,F"Standing here today, it is hard not
OL,15,Fto feel the weight of history on my
OL,16,Fshoulder because the modern
OL,17,Frelationship between our two nations
OL,18,Fand our own peoples spans not merely
OL,19,F250 years, but over four centuries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"It is extraordinary to think that I
OL,7,Fam the nineteenth in our line of
OL,8,Fsovereigns to study, with daily
OL,9,Fattention, the affairs of America.
OL,11,F"So, I come here today with the
OL,12,Fhighest respect for the United States
OL,13,FCongress, this citadel of democracy
OL,14,Fcreated to represent the voice of all
OL,15,FAmerican people to advance sacred
OL,16,Frights and freedoms.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"Speaking in this renowned chamber of
OL,7,Fdebate and deliberation, I cannot help
OL,8,Fbut think of my late mother, Queen
OL,9,FElizabeth, who, in 1991, was also
OL,10,Fafforded this signal honour and
OL,11,Fsimilarly spoke under the watchful eye
OL,12,Fof the Statue of Freedom above us.
OL,14,F"Today, I am here on this great
OL,15,Foccasion in the life of our nations to
OL,16,Fexpress the highest regard and
OL,17,Ffriendship of the British people to
OL,18,Fthe people of the United States.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"As you may know, when I address my
OL,7,Fown Parliament at Westminster, we
OL,8,Fstill follow an age-old tradition and
OL,9,Ftake a member of Parliament 'hostage',
OL,10,Fholding him or her at Buckingham
OL,11,FPalace until I am safely returned.
OL,13,F"These days, we look after our 'guest'
OL,14,Frather well ` to the point that they
OL,15,Foften do not want to leave.
OL,17,F"I don't know, Mr Speaker, if there
OL,18,Fwere any volunteers for that role here
OL,19,Ftoday?
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"As I look back across the centuries,
OL,7,FMr Speaker, there emerge certain
OL,8,Fpatterns, certain self-evident truths
OL,9,Ffrom which we can learn and draw
OL,10,Fmutual strength.
OL,12,F"With the spirit of 1776 in our minds,
OL,13,Fwe can perhaps agree that we do not
OL,14,Falways agree ` at least in the first
OL,15,Finstance.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"Indeed, the very principle on which
OL,7,Fyour Congress was founded ` no
OL,8,Ftaxation without representation ` was
OL,9,Fat once a fundamental disagreement
OL,10,Fbetween us, and at the same time a
OL,11,Fshared democratic value which you
OL,12,Finherited from us.
OL,14,F"Ours is a partnership born out of
OL,15,Fdispute, but no less strong for it, so
OL,16,Fperhaps, in this example, we can
OL,17,Fdiscern that our nations are in fact
OL,18,Finstinctively like-minded ` a product
OL,19,Fof the common democratic, legal and
OL,20,Fsocial traditions in which our
OL,21,Fgovernance is rooted to this day.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"Drawing on these values and
OL,7,Ftraditions, time and again, our two
OL,8,Fcountries have always found ways to
OL,9,Fcome together.
OL,11,F"And by jove, Mr Speaker, when we have
OL,12,Ffound that way to agree, what great
OL,13,Fchange is brought about ` not just for
OL,14,Fthe benefit of our peoples, but of all
OL,15,Fpeoples.
OL,17,F"This, I believe, is the special
OL,18,Fingredient in our relationship.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"As President Trump himself observed
OL,7,Fduring his state visit to Britain last
OL,8,Fautumn, 'The bond of kinship and
OL,9,Fidentity between America and the
OL,10,FUnited Kingdom is priceless and
OL,11,Feternal.
OL,13,F"It is irreplaceable and unbreakable.'
OL,15,F"Mr Speaker, this is by no means my
OL,16,Ffirst visit to Washington DC ` the
OL,17,Fcapital of this great republic.
OL,19,F"It is in fact my 20th visit to the
OL,20,FUnited States, and my first as King
OL,21,Fand head of the Commonwealth.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"This is a city which symbolises a
OL,7,Fperiod in our shared history, or what
OL,8,FCharles Dickens might have called 'A
OL,9,FTale of Two Georges': the first
OL,10,FPresident, George Washington, and my
OL,11,Ffive-times Great Grandfather, King
OL,12,FGeorge III.
OL,14,F"King George never set foot in America
OL,15,Fand, please rest assured, I am not
OL,16,Fhere as part of some cunning rearguard
OL,17,Faction.
OL,19,F"The Founding Fathers were bold and
OL,20,Fimaginative rebels with a cause.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"250 years ago, or, as we say in the
OL,7,FUnited Kingdom 'just the other day',
OL,8,Fthey declared Independence.
OL,10,F"By balancing contending forces and
OL,11,Fdrawing strength in diversity, they
OL,12,Funited 13 disparate colonies to forge
OL,13,Fa nation on the revolutionary idea of
OL,14,F'life, liberty and the pursuit of
OL,15,Fhappiness'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"They carried with them, and carried
OL,7,Fforward, the great inheritance of the
OL,8,FBritish Enlightenment ` as well as the
OL,9,Fideals which had an even deeper
OL,10,Fhistory in English common law and
OL,11,FMagna Carta.
OL,13,F"These roots run deep, and they are
OL,14,Fstill vital.
OL,16,F"Our Declaration of Rights of 1689 was
OL,17,Fnot only the foundation of our
OL,18,Fconstitutional monarchy, but also
OL,19,Fprovided the source of so many of the
OL,20,Fprinciples reiterated, often verbatim,
OL,21,Fin the American Bill of Rights of 1791.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"And those roots go even further back
OL,7,Fin our history: the US Supreme Court
OL,8,FHistorical Society has calculated that
OL,9,FMagna Carta is cited in at least 160
OL,10,FSupreme Court cases since 1789, not
OL,11,Fleast as the foundation of the
OL,12,Fprinciple that executive power is
OL,13,Fsubject to checks and balances.
OL,15,F"This is the reason why there stands a
OL,16,Fstone, by the River Thames at
OL,17,FRunnymede where Magna Carta was signed
OL,18,Fin the year 1215.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"This stone records that an acre of
OL,7,Fthat ancient and historic site was
OL,8,Fgiven to the United States of America
OL,9,Fby the people of the United Kingdom,
OL,10,Fto symbolise our shared resolve in
OL,11,Fsupport of liberty, and in memory of
OL,12,FPresident John F Kennedy.
OL,14,F"Distinguished members of the 119th
OL,15,FCongress, it is here in these very
OL,16,Fhalls that this spirit of liberty and
OL,17,Fthe promise of America's founders is
OL,18,Fpresent in every session and every
OL,19,Fvote cast.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31619
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"Not by the will of one, but by the
OL,7,Fdeliberation of many, representing the
OL,8,Fliving mosaic of the United States.
OL,10,F"In both of our countries, it is the
OL,11,Fvery fact of our vibrant, diverse and
OL,12,Ffree societies that gives us our
OL,13,Fcollective strength, including to
OL,14,Fsupport victims of some of the ills
OL,15,Fthat, so tragically, exist in both our
OL,16,Fsocieties today.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31620
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"And, Mr Speaker, for many here ` and
OL,7,Ffor myself ` the Christian faith is a
OL,8,Ffirm anchor and daily inspiration that
OL,9,Fguides us not only personally, but
OL,10,Ftogether as members of our community.
OL,12,F"Having devoted a large part of my
OL,13,Flife to interfaith relationships and
OL,14,Fgreater understanding, it is that
OL,15,Ffaith in the triumph of light over
OL,16,Fdarkness which I have found confirmed
OL,17,Fcountless times.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31621
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"Through it I am inspired by the
OL,7,Fprofound respect that develops as
OL,8,Fpeople of different faiths grow in
OL,9,Ftheir understanding of each other.
OL,11,F"It is why it is my hope ` my prayer `
OL,12,Fthat, in these turbulent times,
OL,13,Fworking together and with our
OL,14,Finternational partners, we can stem
OL,15,Fthe beating of ploughshares into
OL,16,Fswords.
OL,18,F"I am mindful that we are still in the
OL,19,Fseason of Easter, the season that most
OL,20,Fstrengthens my hope.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31622
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"It is why I believe, with all my
OL,7,Fheart, that the essence of our two
OL,8,Fnations is a generosity of spirit and
OL,9,Fa duty to foster compassion, to
OL,10,Fpromote peace, to deepen mutual
OL,11,Funderstanding and to value all people,
OL,12,Fof all faiths, and of none.
OL,14,F"The alliance that our two nations
OL,15,Fhave built over the centuries, and for
OL,16,Fwhich we are profoundly grateful to
OL,17,Fthe American people, is truly unique.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31623
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"And that alliance is part of what
OL,7,FHenry Kissinger described as Kennedy's
OL,8,F'soaring vision' of an Atlantic
OL,9,Fpartnership based on twin pillars:
OL,10,FEurope and America.
OL,12,F"That partnership, I believe Mr
OL,13,FSpeaker, is more important today than
OL,14,Fit has ever been.
OL,16,F"The first reigning British sovereign
OL,17,Fto set foot in America was my
OL,18,Fgrandfather, King George VI.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31624
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"He visited in 1939 with my beloved
OL,7,Fgrandmother, Queen Elizabeth the Queen
OL,8,FMother.
OL,10,F"The forces of fascism in Europe were
OL,11,Fon the march, and some time before the
OL,12,FUnited States had joined us in the
OL,13,Fdefence of freedom.
OL,15,F"Our shared values prevailed.
OL,17,F"Today, we find ourselves in a new
OL,18,Fera, but those values remain.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G24/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31625
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"It is an era that is, in many ways,
OL,7,Fmore volatile and more dangerous than
OL,8,Fthe world to which my late mother
OL,9,Fspoke, in this chamber, in 1991.
OL,11,F"The challenges we face are too great
OL,12,Ffor any one nation to bear alone.
OL,14,F"But in this unpredictable
OL,15,Fenvironment, our alliance cannot rest
OL,16,Fon past achievements, or assume that
OL,17,Ffoundational principles simply endure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31626
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"As my Prime Minister said last month:
OL,7,F'ours is an indispensable partnership.
OL,8,FWe must not disregard everything that
OL,9,Fhas sustained us for the last eighty
OL,10,Fyears. Instead, we must build on it'.
OL,12,F"Renewal today starts with security.
OL,14,F"The United Kingdom recognises that
OL,15,Fthe threats we face demand a
OL,16,Ftransformation in British defence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31627
SC,0027
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"That is why our country, in order to
OL,7,Fbe fit for the future, has committed
OL,8,Fto the biggest sustained increase in
OL,9,Fdefence spending since the Cold War `
OL,10,Fduring part of which, over 50 years
OL,11,Fago, I served with immense pride in
OL,12,Fthe Royal Navy, following in the naval
OL,13,Ffootsteps of my father, Prince Philip,
OL,14,FDuke of Edinburgh; my grandfather,
OL,15,FKing George VI; my great uncle, Lord
OL,16,FMountbatten; and my great grandfather,
OL,17,FKing George V.
OL,19,F"This year, of course, also marks the
OL,20,F25th anniversary of 9/11.
OL,26,@nD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G27/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31628
SC,0028
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"This atrocity was a defining moment
OL,7,Ffor America and your pain and shock
OL,8,Fwere felt around the whole world.
OL,10,F"During my visit to New York, my wife
OL,11,Fand I will again pay our respects to
OL,12,Fthe victims, the families, and the
OL,13,Fbravery shown in the face of terrible
OL,14,Floss. We stood with you then.
OL,16,F"And we stand with you now in solemn
OL,17,Fremembrance of a day that shall never
OL,18,Fbe forgotten.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G28/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31629
SC,0029
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"In the immediate aftermath of 9/11,
OL,7,Fwhen Nato invoked Article Five for the
OL,8,Ffirst time, and the United Nations
OL,9,FSecurity Council was united in the
OL,10,Fface of terror, we answered the call
OL,11,Ftogether ` as our people have done so
OL,12,Ffor more than a century, shoulder to
OL,13,Fshoulder, through two World Wars, the
OL,14,FCold War, Afghanistan and moments that
OL,15,Fhave defined our shared security.
OL,17,F"Today, Mr Speaker, that same,
OL,18,Funyielding resolve is needed for the
OL,19,Fdefence of Ukraine and her most
OL,20,Fcourageous people.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G29/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31630
SC,0030
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"It is needed in order to secure a
OL,7,Ftruly just and lasting peace.
OL,9,F"From the depths of the Atlantic to
OL,10,Fthe disastrously melting ice-caps of
OL,11,Fthe Arctic, the commitment and
OL,12,Fexpertise of the United States Armed
OL,13,FForces and its allies lie at the heart
OL,14,Fof Nato, pledged to each other's
OL,15,Fdefence, protecting our citizens and
OL,16,Finterests, keeping North Americans and
OL,17,FEuropeans safe from our common
OL,18,Fadversaries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G30/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31631
SC,0031
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"Our defence, intelligence and
OL,7,Fsecurity ties are hardwired together
OL,8,Fthrough relationships measured not in
OL,9,Fyears, but in decades.
OL,11,F"Today, thousands of US service
OL,12,Fpersonnel, defence officials and their
OL,13,Ffamilies are stationed in the United
OL,14,FKingdom, as British personnel serve
OL,15,Fwith equal pride across 30 American
OL,16,Fstates.
OL,18,F"We are building F-35s together.
OL,20,F"And we have agreed the most ambitious
OL,21,Fsubmarine programme in history, Aukus.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G31/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31632
SC,0032
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"And we do so in partnership with
OL,7,FAustralia, a country of which I am
OL,8,Falso immensely proud to serve as
OL,9,Fsovereign.
OL,11,F"We do not embark on these remarkable
OL,12,Fendeavours together out of sentiment.
OL,14,F"We do so because they build greater
OL,15,Fshared resilience for the future, so
OL,16,Fmaking our citizens safer for
OL,17,Fgenerations to come.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G32/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31633
SC,0033
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"Our common ideals were not only
OL,7,Fcrucial for liberty and equality, they
OL,8,Fare also the foundation of our shared
OL,9,Fprosperity.
OL,11,F"The rule of law: the certainty of
OL,12,Fstable and accessible rules, an
OL,13,Findependent judiciary resolving
OL,14,Fdisputes and delivering impartial
OL,15,Fjustice.
OL,17,F"These features created the conditions
OL,18,Ffor centuries of unmatched economic
OL,19,Fgrowth in our two countries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G33/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31634
SC,0034
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"This is why our governments are
OL,7,Fconcluding new economic and technology
OL,8,Fagreements ` to write the next chapter
OL,9,Fof our joint prosperity and ensure
OL,10,Fthat British and American ingenuity
OL,11,Fcontinues to lead the world.
OL,13,F"Our nations are combining talent and
OL,14,Fresources in the technologies of
OL,15,Ftomorrow: our new partnerships in
OL,16,Fnuclear fusion and quantum computing,
OL,17,Fand in AI and drug discovery, holding
OL,18,Fthe promise of saving countless lives.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G34/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31635
SC,0035
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"More broadly, we celebrate the 430
OL,7,Fbillion dollars in annual trade that
OL,8,Fcontinues to grow, the 1.7 trillion
OL,9,Fdollars in mutual investment that
OL,10,Ffuels that innovation, and the
OL,11,Fmillions of jobs on both sides of the
OL,12,FAtlantic supported across both
OL,13,Feconomies.
OL,15,F"These are strong foundations on which
OL,16,Fto continue to build, for generations
OL,17,Fyet unborn.
OL,19,F"Our ties in education, research, and
OL,20,Fcultural exchange empower citizens and
OL,21,Ffuture leaders of both countries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G35/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31636
SC,0036
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"The Marshall Scholarship, named after
OL,7,Fthe great General George Marshall, and
OL,8,Fthe Association of which I am so proud
OL,9,Fto be patron, are emblematic of the
OL,10,Fconnection between our two countries.
OL,12,F"Since its founding, more than 2,300
OL,13,Fscholarships have been awarded,
OL,14,Fopening doors for Americans from all
OL,15,Fwalks of life to study at the United
OL,16,FKingdom's leading universities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G36/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31637
SC,0037
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"So as we look toward the next 250
OL,7,Fyears, we must also reflect on our
OL,8,Fshared responsibility to safeguard
OL,9,Fnature, our most precious and
OL,10,Firreplaceable asset.
OL,12,F"Millennia before our nations existed,
OL,13,Fbefore any border drawn, the mountains
OL,14,Fof Scotland and Appalachia were one, a
OL,15,Fsingle, continuous range, forged in
OL,16,Fthe ancient collision of continents.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G37/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31638
SC,0038
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"The natural wonders of the United
OL,7,FStates of America are indeed a unique
OL,8,Fasset, and generations of Americans
OL,9,Fhave risen to this calling:
OL,10,Findigenous, political and civic
OL,11,Fleaders, people in rural communities
OL,12,Fand cities alike, have all helped to
OL,13,Fprotect and nurture what President
OL,14,FTheodore Roosevelt called 'the
OL,15,Fglorious heritage' of this land's
OL,16,Fextraordinary natural splendour, on
OL,17,Fwhich so much of its prosperity has
OL,18,Falways depended.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G38/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31639
SC,0039
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777479067
OL,3,CIn full: King Charles' historic speech
OL,4,Cto Congress
OL,6,F"Yet even as we celebrate the beauty
OL,7,Fthat surrounds us, our generation must
OL,8,Fdecide how to address the collapse of
OL,9,Fcritical natural systems which
OL,10,Fthreatens far more than the harmony
OL,11,Fand essential diversity of nature.
OL,13,F"We ignore at our peril the fact that
OL,14,Fthese natural systems, in other words,
OL,15,Fnature's own economy, provide the
OL,16,Ffoundation for our prosperity and our
OL,17,Fnational security.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G39/43
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
